You can devide your menu on four main parts:
[list][*][b]The top dock[/b]: Where you can easily launch your favourite apps.
[*][b]The desktop[/b]: Where your apps will appear and where you can have shortcuts and files
[*][b]The system bar[/b]: Where you can do some common actions.
[*][b]The bottom bar[/b]: Where you can see your open apps and see the time.
[/list]